      "content": "it really does feel like there's no path forward. like i'm just stuck in this loop of hurting. i look at the future and there's just nothing there. just more of this silence. i wonder if anyone even notices how much it hurts, or if the world just keeps spinning like it doesn't matter that my whole world ended.",
